{"kind":"symbol","identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/WorkflowUI\/documentation\/WorkflowUI\/UIKit\/UIViewController\/environment","interfaceLanguage":"swift"},"schemaVersion":{"minor":3,"major":0,"patch":0},"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/WorkflowUI\/documentation\/WorkflowUI","doc:\/\/WorkflowUI\/documentation\/WorkflowUI\/UIKit","doc:\/\/WorkflowUI\/documentation\/WorkflowUI\/UIKit\/UIViewController"]]},"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"platforms":["iOS"],"tokens":[{"text":"var","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"environment","kind":"identifier"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"preciseIdentifier":"s:15ViewEnvironmentAAV","text":"ViewEnvironment","kind":"typeIdentifier","identifier":"doc:\/\/WorkflowUI\/documentation\/WorkflowUI\/ViewEnvironment"},{"text":" { ","kind":"text"},{"text":"get","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" }","kind":"text"}],"languages":["swift"]}]},{"kind":"content","content":[{"type":"heading","text":"Discussion","level":2,"anchor":"discussion"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"If you’d like to provide overrides for the environment as it flows through a node, you should conform to","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"code":"ViewEnvironmentObserving","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" and provide those overrides in ","type":"text"},{"code":"customize(environment:)","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":". E.g.:","type":"text"}]},{"type":"codeListing","syntax":"swift","code":["func customize(environment: inout ViewEnvironment) {","    environment.traits.mode = .dark","}"]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"By default, this property gets the environment by recursively walking to the root of the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"propagation path, and applying customizations on the way back down. The invalidation path may be"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"interrupted if a node has set it’s "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"environmentAncestor"},{"type":"text","text":" to "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"nil"},{"type":"text","text":", even if there is a node"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"which specifies this node as an "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"environmentDescendant"},{"type":"text","text":"."}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"If you’d like to update the return value of this variable and have those changes propagated through the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"propagation hierarchy, conform to "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"ViewEnvironmentObserving"},{"type":"text","text":" and call "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"setNeedsEnvironmentUpdate()"},{"type":"text","text":" and wait"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"for the system to call "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"apply(context:)"},{"type":"text","text":" when appropriate (e.g. on the next layout pass for"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"UIViewController"},{"type":"text","text":"\/"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"UIView"},{"type":"text","text":" subclasses)."}]},{"type":"aside","style":"important","name":"Important","content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"UIViewController"},{"text":" and ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"UIView"},{"text":" conformers ","type":"text"},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"text":"must","type":"text"}]},{"text":" call ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"applyEnvironmentIfNeeded()"},{"text":" in","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"viewWillLayoutSubviews()"},{"type":"text","text":" and "},{"code":"layoutSubviews()","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" respectively."}]}]}]}],"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/workflowui\/uikit\/uiviewcontroller\/environment"]}],"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"The "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"ViewEnvironment"},{"type":"